Privacy Policy

MathRush does not collect personal data directly.

However, the app uses third-party services such as Google AdMob 
to display advertisements. These services may collect anonymous 
usage data, device identifiers, advertising identifiers, crash 
reports, and performance information to improve ad relevance 
and app stability.

Information collected may include:

- Device identifiers
- Advertising data
- Usage statistics
- Crash diagnostics
- Performance data

This information is managed by Google according to their 
privacy policies.

Google Privacy Policy:
https://policies.google.com/privacy

The app does not sell personal data.

If you have any questions:
contact@yourdomain.com
